{
  "texts": [
    "Software developers adopt co-pilots, interpreters, and private or automated GPT models to optimize tools and workflows.",
    "The rapid introduction of these is pressuring existing co-creation processes such as agile or DevOps.",
    "Machine learning and NLP aid code discovery, production, review, testing, configuration, and optimization.",
    "In automation, simultaneous forces at play affect productivity (Elazhary 2021).",
    "Continuous process development has been the answer for decades, with many doctrines, e.g., \"write once, copy endlessly,\" \"customer in a loop,\" \"code and test simultaneously,\" \"test-driven development,\" and \"create and share.\""
  ]
}